ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 217, British Columbia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 217 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of BRITISH COLUMBIA, with respect to the severe flooding that occurred from April 26, 2018 to May 24, 2018.
